@node "bugs" "Known Bugs"

Do not try to run from 'Ram Disk:' or any other Device with two names..

Do not make Storage Dir to a device with Two names as device name...

 If you want to store in Ram Disk: change it to Ram: in the config 
 before you save.....

A bug in IBrowse rexx will not close IBrowse safley. so you need to 
  manually close IBrowse.

The quit will not close multiview, as multiview seems to hang when 
closing via rexx....

A memory leak was reported when letting SpymasTer run over a period of
Time using Visage.. i have emailed Visage arthur, but no reply as of
yet...

do not quit when delay or downloading.. muirexx will crash.....

if you quit and the gui does not exit try the X......

if spymaster encounters an error with a site.... and you get errors via CON:
   close the con and hit X.. and restart spymaster....



@endnode
