@node "Hist" "History"

26.10.97 v1.0

First public release

29.10.97 v1.1

Changed Command poplist to buttons
 (Start = double click on site)

Fixed front page Delay time it now adjustable without being resest.....

Buttons & What they do

ABORT = Abort will stop the current download and exit program loop

STOP = will Stop the program loop after current download/or reset delay to 0
       and exit loop

PICSAVE = if manual save it turned on this allows you to save current Pic to 
          defined Picture Store Area.

End = Will set the Delay Timer to 0 and start the next download..... 


New Config options::

Do Ask/Do Not Ask  = if file exists do you want a requestor to pop up ask you 
                     what to do or Do Not Ask will just download even if files
                     exists.

IB on Workbench= IB will open on workbench......
IB on Custom = IB will open on your custom screen if you have defined...

Change the visage_options alittle Enter any Visage shell option in the box 
provide.....:)

Added Fastview Options (tested with Fastview v2.0) Same as visage add a 
Options box so any valid shell command can be used and added.....

Removed the Quit for people that don't read the *&&@#$ Manual...:)

Added Hide to pulldown and also GUI quit button....

Quit button will try and exit the GUI...may take a few secs.....

YOu need to Edit Tool path in the Spymaster Icon....Define the path for 
 Muirexx


30.10.97 v1.2

Ok... a bug in 1.1 with visage is fixed...

the multivew opitions needs WINDOW PORT=SPYMASTER


03.11.97 v1.3ß

Add Smart delay... Take the Download time and minuses it from 
Site Delay to get the Delay time..

Fixed the adjustable delay on front page...

Also rewrote all the requestors to use rexxreqtools.library instead of 
muirexx,, which was causing alot of SYSTEM ALERTS......

Also reworte the Quit,,

****************IMPORTANT*************************

Emergency Exit: If you quit and it does not quit try this in a shell:

 rx "setclip('SPYMASTER_DCOMP','COMPLETE')"

use only in a emergency......:)

05.11.97 v1.3 Public release

This will be the last public release unless a bug is found other than the
Ram Disk: bug......as I'm going to start on a multiple session version for 
users that support the program......

20.12.97 v1.4 Public release

ADDED browse and Browse loop.....

Added user defined view.. so any shell/cli viewer should work....

so just give viewer path and any shell options you would like in the config


BROWSE-  shift-select as many sites as you would like to view in one pass

LOOP -   Shift-select as many sites as you would like to view in a loop

X - this is emergency exit use in an emergency..........

To exit make you you abort the download or quit the timer then quit..

give quit about 20 secs after it says exiting... if it doesn't exit

try the X.....


also use the X if and error occurs and it say spymaster is working....

OK.. on the config page is another timer.... this is for the browse loop how 
much time to wait before going on to next site....

well i just suffered a HD crash so new web pages well not be done for this release..

but the address will be www.erols.com/bosman/spymaster/


@endnode
